      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZA DUANE (4) jumped favourite and was too quick with an all-the-way win last start (21.92) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 383m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Hard to fault his recent form and can win again. BLUE MARGUERITE (7) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing fifth (18.44) at this track last time. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Key runner on best form. INFRARED POWER (1) is suited by the inside draw. Last start finished 3rd on March 8 over 312m at this track behind MUM KNOWS BEST beaten 3 lengths (18.56) in a Grade 3/4. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. MUM KNOWS BEST (5) has strong credentials at this circuit over this journey.",
